title: Priceless: Hillary Clinton sends Rand Paul a copy of her book. He writes an inscription and sells it... | Opinion - Conservative
text:
(Before It's News)
Here’s what the inscription says :
Hillary, your refusal to provide security for our mission in Benghazi should forever preclude you from higher office!
Rand Paul signed Hillary Clinton’s book and is now auctioning it off, along w/ his own book https://t.co/ce2s9ImR6M pic.twitter.com/WW1fGg7fmZ
— Ashley Killough (@KilloughCNN) October 7, 2015
